title: Premier League: Roy Keane on Rooney's China move - "It's madness!"
text: Tweet Share Wayne Rooney is linked with a move to China, but Roy Keane feels that is the wrong move for the Manchester United captain. More Manchester United great Roy Keane believes it would be "madness" for Wayne Rooney to make a move to China. Rooney, 31, continues to be linked with a lucrative switch to the Chinese Super League, having found himself on the outer at United. But that has left former United team-mate Keane bemused, with the Irishman saying the club and England captain should be staying in Europe.
